statement.p:
Find a formula for the inverse of the function 
			g: \mathbb{Z}_{29} \rightarrow  \mathbb{Z}_{29}
			 where g(a)= 5\times_{29}a +_{29}25.  Suggestion:  You can use the symbols \times and + in your work instead of \times_{29} and +_{29} as long as we agree that they stand for mod 29 operations.
